701379f-a.title: Bronx: Kingsbridge Avenue - 231st Street (West)
701379f-a.text:
Kingsbridge Avenue, west side, north from W. 231st Street,
to W. 232nd Street. At the N.W. corner of W. 232nd Street is
visible Public School No. 7.
About 1923
Joseph P. Day
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS
